import React from "react"; import { NavLink } from "react-router-dom"; import Header from '../Header/Header.js' import Title from '../Title/Title.js' import active from '../img/active.png' import archive from '../img/archive.png' const Analytics = () => { return (
<div className='side-col'> <NavLink className='side-col-links' to='/journal'> Create New Journal Entry </NavLink> <NavLink className='side-col-links' to='/archived-thoughts'> Thoughts let go <img src={archive}></img> </NavLink> <NavLink className='side-col-links' to='/active-thoughts'> Active thoughts <img src={active}></img> </NavLink> </div> </div> ) } export default Analytics
